page.title: 20Compilers of this Project
page.content: The information in this section of the Domesday Project was collected by children in Class 5 at Great Doddington Primary School in June 1985. They were: Neil Abbott, Peggy Arch, Jennifer Blackwell, Neil Catling, Ruth Cooper, Nathan Crisp, Johnny Digby, Karin Duffy, Becky Elliott, Deborah Jackson, Anthony Jennings, Katharine Johnson, Louise Kellingray, Rachel Large, Anthony Martin, Christopher Mills, Thomas Mitchell, Caroline Moore, Sally Sharp, Sally Sneddon, Kirsty Thompson, Shelley Tomalin, Andrew Tomkins, Lynda Tomkins and Emma Weaver.
